          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1384.-Step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>onion</strong> has softened, add the<strong> chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>dried</strong> <strong>oregano</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and<strong> tomato paste</strong> and cook for 1 min  </p>",
